{
  "texts": [
    "For instance, OpenAI utilized transformers in their language models (OpenAI 2021), and DeepMind employed them in the development of AlphaStar (DeepMind 2021).",
    "In order for models to effectively perform sequence transduction, it is crucial to understand the dependencies and connections within a given input, such as a sentence.",
    "Recurrent Neural Networks (RNNs) and Convolutional Neural Networks (CNNs) have been commonly used for this purpose due to their inherent properties.",
    "However, they also have limitations.",
    "RNNs struggle with longer input sentences as they tend to lose context for words that are distant from the current word being processed."
  ]
}